# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HWAX Portal — routing destinations.   Format:  <system-id>=<URL>
#
# Set a system's URL here → its tile becomes clickable and opens that URL (new tab).
# Leave it commented → the tile stays "coming_soon".
# The names/logos/descriptions live in systems.yaml; ONLY the destination is here.
#
# After editing, the portal picks it up on next start, or instantly via:
#   POST /systems/reload   (admin)
#
# dev = your local ports.  prod = the real URLs (use a separate file via ROUTES_PATH,
# or override any line with an env var:  SYS_HEAX_HUB_URL=https://...).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Uncomment + set the port each project's frontend is running on:

# heax-hub=http://localhost:9301
# ai-data-hub=http://localhost:9302
# mx-white-paper=http://localhost:9303
# report-archive=http://localhost:9304
# smart-twin-cluster=http://localhost:9305
# spdm=http://localhost:9306
